## âœ¨ Features

| Feature                                | Description                                             |
| -------------------------------------- | ------------------------------------------------------- |
| ğŸ§  **Custom RAG Engine**               | Pure Python implementation of retrieval + generation.   |
| ğŸ” **Dual Validation (Groq + OpenAI)** | Cross-verifies answers before auto-learning.            |
| ğŸ“š **Auto-Learning System**            | Automatically promotes correct answers into Pinecone.   |
| ğŸŒ **Cloud + Local Mode**              | Toggle between Groq (cloud) or Ollama (local).          |
| ğŸ§© **Context-Aware Chat**              | Fetches relevant DSA context dynamically.               |
| ğŸ’¬ **Streamlit UI**                    | Interactive tutor interface with chat history and logs. |
| ğŸ›¡ï¸ **Safety Filter**                   | Blocks non-DSA and irrelevant topics.                   |

